dil chahta hai ( english : the heart desires ) is a 2001 indian comedy-drama film starring aamir khan , saif ali khan , akshaye khanna , preity zinta , sonali kulkarni , and dimple kapadia .   the first film written and directed by farhan akhtar , it is set in modern-day urban mumbai and sydney , and focuses on a major period of transition in the lives of three young friends .   in 2001 , the film won national film award for best feature film in hindi .   it performed better in the urban areas of the country compared to the rural areas , which was attributed by critics to the city-oriented lifestyle depicted in which all the characters are from rich or upper-middle-class families .   over the years , it has attained a cult status .